data.meta_description: Information about the American Association independent professional baseball league and its member teams and league news

data.text:
The American Association has 12 teams across the United States and Canada. Here is the league’s official website:

https://aabaseball.com

Games can be watched via subscription service at: https://www.aabaseball.tv/

The league has 12 teams for the 2021 season. These include:

Chicago Dogs

Cleburne Railroaders

Fargo-Moorhead RedHawks

Gary Southshore RailCats

Kane County Cougars

Kansas City Monarchs

Lake Country Dockhounds

Lincoln Saltdogs

Milwaukee Milkmen

Sioux City Explorers

Sioux Falls Canaries

Winnipeg Goldeyes
